I"r<h2 id="add-id">add id</h2>

<p>to add a specific class, place <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">{: .className}</code> under it</p>

<div class="language-md highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>sentence with id
{: #supId}

</code></pre></div></div>

<p>here <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;p id='supId'&gt;sentence with id&lt;/p&gt;</code></p>

<h2 id="add-class">add class</h2>

<p>to add a specific class, place <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">{: .className}</code> under it</p>

<div class="language-md highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="gu">### title with class</span>
{: .supClass}

</code></pre></div></div>

<p>here <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;h3 class='supClass'&gt;title with class&lt;/h3&gt;</code></p>
